DataElement.preferredName: Protocol Treatment Arm Target Accrual Number Range ISO21090.URG.INT.NONNEG.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A range of integers specifying the minimum and maximum number of subjects to be accrued for the arm. NOTE(S): This may represent the minimum number of subjects needed to support data analysis and/or the maximum number of subjects that may be accrued to this arm.
